      "content": "honestly i can barely get out of bed lately. every time i look at the news or see the climate stats it just feels like we're all just walking around in a burning building. like why even bother with school or a career or anything if the world is just gonna be uninhabitable in a few decades? it feels so pointless to keep building a life when the foundation is literally rotting.",
